Merge pull request #43 from nirvik66/bugfix/change-normaltext-programatically

Fix bug related to issue #37 (mNormalText)

Fix bug related to issue #37. When the normal text is changed programatically it's not appropiately set when the button changes back to the normal state, instead of using the last normal text it's using the one defined on the xml

1. Added custom app icon
2. Updated README file

Version 1.0.3
* Added focused and selected states
Updated project build files for IntelliJ IDEA 14

1. Added library description file for About AboutLibraries
2. Increased version to 1.0.2
Fixed buggy behavior when an endless button gets re-sized #14
Moved sdk properties to gradle.properties file

Version 1.0.0
* Fixed issue: Button padding are ignored #11
* Added prefix 'pb_' for all custom attributes to avoid conflict #12

Merge branch 'master' into dev

Conflicts:
	gradle.properties
	library/src/main/res/values/colors.xml
Added prefix 'pb_' for all custom attributes to avoid conflict #12
Fixed issue: Button padding are ignored #11
Added ActionProcessButton endless loading indicator colors for API 10+

Version 0.0.7
* Added api 10 compatibility
* Fixed bug in ProgressGenerator class

Merge pull request #10 from thefabulous/dev

Added api 10 compatibility
Fixed project name typo, increased version code & version name

Added error state to ProcessButton:
- error state [-1]

Re-factored ProcessButton:
- now state depends on progress:
- - normal state [0]
- - progress state [1-99]
- - success state [100]
- added abstract `drawProgress` method to simplify creating child buttons

Added new attribute to control button corner roundness:

cornerRadius

Renamed styles attributes:

 progressText -> textProgress
 completeText -> textComplete
Fixed bug when all buttons where sharing the same drawable state
Replaced android support library with maven dependency

Updated sample project:
- Now contain main activity with listed samples

1. Moved logic related to flat design to FlatButton class
2. Moved logic related to progress to ProcessButton class
3. Implemented intermediate progress indicator for ActionProcessButton
4. Increased version to 0.0.2
